title: Ep. 355 - Fake News: From Feminism To Foreign Policy
description:
From the foreign policy establishment to third wave feminists, fake news explodes like a North Korean nuke. We will separate fact from fiction. Then, Eric Swalwell’s parody of a presidential campaign is running out of money, and President Trump takes the presidential reality TV show to Japan. Date: 5-28-2019
